# Admin Panel

## Stack
- Frontend: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite 8 + shadcn/ui 4 + Tailwind 4 + React Query 5
- Backend: FastAPI under `app/admin/` (API + session auth)
- Built SPA is committed to `app/admin/static/`

## Conventions
- API changes → `app/admin/api/*`; UI → `admin-panel/src/`.
- Reuse existing shadcn components in `admin-panel/src/components/ui/`.
- Auth: session cookie; brute-force protection via Redis.
- After UI changes: `npm run build` in `admin-panel/`, copy/output into `app/admin/static/`, restart **admin only** (prefer flat `docker restart`, not compose, if worker is up).

## Do not
- Expose secrets in SPA.
- Broaden admin bind/port without owner approval (security sensitive).
- Restart worker when only admin changed.
